'''佩埃特河'''（{{lang-en|Payette River}}）是[[美国|美国]][[斯内克河|斯内克河]]的一条[[支流|支流]]，位于[[爱达荷州|爱达荷州]]西南部，长约{{convert|82.7|mi|km|adj=mid}}<ref name=NHD>U.S. Geological Survey. National Hydrography Dataset high-resolution flowline data. [http://viewer.nationalmap.gov/viewer/ The National Map] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/66gupqQDM?url=http://viewer.nationalmap.gov/viewer/ |date=20120405064000 |dateformat=iso }}, accessed May 3, 2011</ref>。佩埃特河起源于{{link-en|索图斯岭|Sawtooth Range (Idaho)}}和{{link-en|萨蒙河山脉|Salmon River Mountains}}，自东向西穿过[[斯内克河平原|斯内克河平原]]西部，在[[佩埃特县|佩埃特县]][[佩埃特_(愛達荷州)|佩埃特]]汇入[[斯内克河|斯内克河]]，流域面积{{convert|3240|sqmi|km2}}<ref>{{cite web |title=North Fork Payette River Subbasin Assessment |publisher=Idaho Department of Environmental Quality |url=http://www.deq.state.id.us/water/data_reports/surface_water/tmdls/payette_river_sf/payette_river_sf_entire.pdf |accessdate=20 January 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091002014808/http://www.deq.state.id.us/water/data_reports/surface_water/tmdls/payette_river_sf/payette_river_sf_entire.pdf |archivedate=2009-10-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

